# Dashboard screenshots and exports
1. Trend Analysis
Temperature trends over time (monthly/yearly)
Rainfall patterns across seasons
Long-term climate change indicators


2. Anomaly Detection
Identify unusually hot/cold days
Detect extreme weather events (e.g., storms, droughts)


3. Seasonal Analysis
Compare climate metrics across seasons
Visualize average temperature and rainfall by month


4. Geospatial Analysis
Compare climate data across regions or cities
Map temperature or precipitation using heatmaps


5. Correlation Analysis
Relationship between temperature and humidity
Impact of wind speed on temperature or rainfall


6. Forecasting (Optional)
Use time series models (ARIMA, Prophet) to predict future temperature or rainfall


7. Dashboard Creation
Build interactive dashboards using Power BI, Tableau, or Python (Plotly/Dash)
